try: it is block is used to monitor the statements which might cause the exceptions

catch: is must be followed by try block , it is used to catch the exceptions, in paranthesis we need to write which exception is this catch is going to handle

throw; it is used to throw the exceptions manually by the programmer

finally: is block which executes always even if exception is not raised, it used to cleaning purpose

throws: is used to declare the at method defination level to indicate the called of the function should handle the exceptions